  {
    name: "Lingyan Kong",
    quote:
      "Found Joe based on the online reviews and it has been a very pleasant journey since! He's very genuine, kind, punctual, pay attention to details, and professional! Highly recommend him to any of your house projects, small or large.",
    image:
      "https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/66e08c96738392d8929bbf50/66e89f4e868f580ae2bc3393_kong.png",
    imageAlt:
      "Circular blue-gray icon with a white uppercase letter L in the center",
    reviewUrl:
      "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUNqOHJ6LUJREAE!2m1!1s0x0:0x5d541e82cadce9ac!3m1!1s2@1:CIHM0ogKEICAgICj8rz-BQ%7CCgwIvaSLsQYQqMicqwE%7C",
  },
  {
    name: "Vincent Gold",
    quote:
      "Joe and his team exceeded our expectations. They were professional, communicative, and delivered high-quality work. From the initial estimate to the final result, Joe was punctual, and ensured our renovation project was completed to our satisfaction. His attention to detail and work ethic are unmatched.",
    image:
      "https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/66e08c96738392d8929bbf50/66e8a175fd78bb76732c17bf_vincent%20gold.png",
    imageAlt: "Person wearing dark hoodie and sunglasses",
    reviewUrl:
      "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUR5LTVIRWtBRRAB!2m1!1s0x0:0x5d541e82cadce9ac!3m1!1s2@1:CIHM0ogKEICAgIDy-5HEkAE%7CCgwIja7RggYQ8IH6gwE%7C",
  },
  {
    name: "Kara Pydynkowski",
    quote:
      "Joe and his team exceeded our expectations with their kitchen remodel. They were thorough, communicative, and respectful of our space. Their attention to detail was impressive. We enjoyed working with them and would highly recommend NW Development Contracting.",
    image:
      "https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/66e08c96738392d8929bbf50/66e89e0614ece81d677a2cb9_kara%20Pydynkowski.png",
    imageAlt:
      "Woman holding a plate with a pink-frosted doughnut near her mouth, smiling",
    reviewUrl:
      "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUMycEp1ODN3RRAB!2m1!1s0x0:0x5d541e82cadce9ac!3m1!1s2@1:CIHM0ogKEICAgIC2pJu83wE%7CCgwIkvnYkgYQ8J-twAI%7C",
