  {
    name: "Crystal Trulove",
    quote:
      "We hired Joe for his attention to detail and cost-saving suggestions. He was communicative, flexible, and professional throughout the process. The crew did excellent work and left the site spotless. We highly recommend NW Development Contracting.",
    image:
      "https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/66e08c96738392d8929bbf50/66e89eb9f538d2eddcc659b5_crystal%20trulove.png",
    imageAlt:
      "Smiling woman with glasses and shoulder-length light brown hair wearing a blue top",
    reviewUrl:
      "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUNibUt6S1ZREAE!2m1!1s0x0:0x5d541e82cadce9ac!3m1!1s2@1:CIHM0ogKEICAgICbmKzKVQ%7CCgwIkoH8tAYQwPLqwwE%7C",
  },
  {
    name: "Sara Nicolas",
    quote:
      "Couldn't have asked for a better experience! Joe and his crew were patient with me and answered all of my questions before and during my projects. They were able to accommodate my time sensitive timeline and exceeded my expectations. I would recommend them to any of my friends and family for their projects ❤️",
    image:
      "https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/66e08c96738392d8929bbf50/66e89f9a1f4513365448a8c2_sara%20nicolas.png",
    imageAlt:
      "Smiling woman with curly dark hair wearing a red patterned blouse",
    reviewUrl:
      "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUREaUwzOUZREAE!2m1!1s0x0:0x5d541e82cadce9ac!3m1!1s2@1:CIHM0ogKEICAgIDDiL39FQ%7CCgwI1dm8sAYQ6PbIrAE%7C",
  },
  {
    name: "Keith Babiasz",
    quote:
      "Joe and his crew remodeled our kitchen beautifully and on time. They communicated well, and everything went as promised. We love our kitchen and would hire them again.",
